{"tha-ap219:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap219:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap219:0.3":"Talavantadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap219:1.1":"“Talavantam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap219:1.2":"tissassadiccabandhuno; ","tha-ap219:1.3":"Gimhanibbapanatthaya, ","tha-ap219:1.4":"parilahopasantiya. ","tha-ap219:2.1":"Sannibbapemi ragaggim, ","tha-ap219:2.2":"dosagginca taduttarim; ","tha-ap219:2.3":"Nibbapemi ca mohaggim, ","tha-ap219:2.4":"talavantassidam phalam. ","tha-ap219:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap219:3.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap219:3.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap219:3.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap219:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap219:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap219:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap219:4.4":"talavantassidam phalam. ","tha-ap219:5.1":"Tesatthimhi ito kappe, ","tha-ap219:5.2":"mahanamasanamako; ","tha-ap219:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap219:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap219:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap219:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap219:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap219:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma talavantadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap219:8.1":"Talavantadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}